de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces.businessrules.server

Interface IServerObjectsControl


  • public interface IServerObjectsControl
    Contains store, delete and load functions for main objects like customers, cases, questions ... The objects can be manipulated directly before or after the database actions.
    was:
    ServerObjectsControl.java
